</a></i></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%;background: #EEEEEE;\">Symphonies</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Symphony_No._1_(Glass)\" title=\"Symphony No. 1 (Glass)\">Symphony No. 1 (<i>Low</i>)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Symphony_No._2_(Glass)\" title=\"Symphony No. 2 (Glass)\">Symphony No. 2</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Symphony_No._3_(Glass)\" title=\"Symphony No. 3 (Glass)\">Symphony No. 3</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Symphony_No._4_(Glass)\" title=\"Symphony No. 4 (Glass)\">Symphony No. 4 (<i>Heroes</i>)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Symphony_No._5_(Glass)\" title=\"Symphony No. 5 (Glass)\">Symphony No. 5 (<i>Choral</i>)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Symphony_No._6_(Glass)\" title=\"Symphony No. 6 (Glass)\">Symphony No. 6 (<i>Plutonian Ode</i>)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Symphony_No._7_(Glass)\" title=\"Symphony No. 7 (Glass)\">Symphony No. 7 (<i>A Toltec Symphony</i>)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Symphony_No._8_(Glass)\" title=\"Symphony No. 8 (Glass)\">Symphony No. 8</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Symphony_No._9_(Glass)\" title=\"Symphony No. 9 (Glass)\">Symphony No. 9</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Symphony_No._10_(Glass)\" title=\"Symphony No. 10 (Glass)\">Symphony No. 10</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Symphony_No._11_(Glass)\" title=\"Symphony No. 11 (Glass)\">Symphony No. 11</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Symphony_No._12_(Glass)\" title=\"Symphony No. 12 (Glass)\">Symphony No. 12</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%;background: #EEEEEE;\">Concertos</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Tirol_Concerto_for_Piano_and_Orchestra\" title=\"Tirol Concerto for Piano and Orchestra\">Piano Concerto No. 1 (<i>Tirol</i>)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Piano_Concerto_No._2_(Glass)\" title=\"Piano Concerto No. 2 (Glass)\">Piano Concerto No. 2 (<i>After Lewis and Clark</i>)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Harpsichord_Concerto_(Glass)\" title=\"Harpsichord Concerto (Glass)\">Harpsichord Concerto</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Violin_Concerto_(Glass)\" title=\"Violin Concerto (Glass)\">Violin Concerto (withdrawn)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Violin_Concerto_No._1_(Glass)\" title=\"Violin Concerto No. 1 (Glass)\">Violin Concerto No. 1</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Violin_Concerto_No._2_(Glass)\" title=\"Violin Concerto No. 2 (Glass)\">Violin Concerto No. 2 (<i>American Four Seasons</i>)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Cello_Concerto_No._1_(Glass)\" title=\"Cello Concerto No. 1 (Glass)\">Cello Concerto No. 1</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Concerto_Fantasy_for_Two_Timpanists_and_Orchestra\" title=\"Concerto Fantasy for Two Timpanists and Orchestra\">Concerto Fantasy for Two Timpanists and Orchestra</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%;background: #EEEEEE;\">Related articles</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_compositions_by_Philip_Glass\" title=\"List of compositions by Philip Glass\">List of compositions by Philip Glass</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Philip_Glass_Ensemble\" title=\"Philip Glass Ensemble\">Philip Glass Ensemble</a></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Glass:_A_Portrait_of_Philip_in_Twelve_Parts\" title=\"Glass: A Portrait of Philip in Twelve Parts\">Glass: A Portrait of Philip in Twelve Parts</a></i></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Minimal_music\" title=\"Minimal music\">Minimal music</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Robert_Wilson_(director)\" title=\"Robert Wilson (directo